law.text: A self-insured employer-organized association group shall notify the commissioner immediately of any change in the information required to be filed under KRS 304.17A-808 or 304.17A-812.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1262, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 78, sec. 8, effective June 24, 2003.
